items.title: Add short twig runes to lettersToRunes
items.body:
Currently always transcribes text to long twig runes. Note: runes to text does transform short twigs too, does not need edits.

- Offer separate functions for separate rune sets.
- Alter current exported method to accept rune dialect, which defaults to current long branch. Keeps backwards compatibility.

items.title: Check SWC as alternative to TypeScript default build
items.body:
SWC seems to support almost everything nowadays. Check it out as alternative build step to:

- Maybe get easy minify, compress, and mangled release.
- Support Rust based alternatives

In case of larger hardcoded sets of TS objects the minification would probably be notable benefit.

items.title: Some entries only have example block
items.body:
Generally definition is either in a) definition or in b) sense group.

Seems some words (like "öykähytteä") only have example blocks, which roughly contain the definition.

Use first example as definition if:
- No definition
- No sense groups
- Has examples
